      • expandNamesList

        public static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,Names.LookupType> expandNamesList(Session session,
                                                                   java.util.TreeSet<java.lang.String> searchfor,
                                                                   java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,Names.LookupType> searched)
        Fully expands a list of name strings. Searches all public address books available to the specified session for person or group entries. For every group found the members of the group will be checked against the searched set. If not in the searched list they will also be searched for (and added to the searched list). Found group members will be included in the results.
        Parameters:
        session - Session in effect for the search.
        searchfor - Set of name strings for which to search.
        searched - Set of name strings which have already been searched.
        Returns:
        Set of all expanded found names & group members. K = name string, V = Result type (Person, Group, Unknown)

      • expandNamesList

        public static java.util.TreeSet<java.lang.String> expandNamesList(Session session,
                                                  java.lang.Object source,
                                                  Names.LookupType... filters)
        Fully expands a list of name strings. Searches all public address books available to the specified session for person or group entries. For every group found the members of the group will also be searched for and included in the results.
        Parameters:
        session - Session in effect for the search.
        source - Object which can be converted to a TreeSet of Strings for which to search.
        filters - Names.LookupType (Person, Group, Unknown) for which to limit the results.
        Returns:
        Set of all expanded found names & group members whose result type is included in filters. K = name string, V = Result type (Person, Group, Unknown)

      • expandNamesList
